Description:
Some pirates are busy looting a place full of boxes and packages, seemingly unaware of your presence. 

You can barely make out the symbol on the crates, but it appears to be an old version of the COT seal. 

It's unclear how this load ended up here, but if it contains anything valuable, those pirates will get to it before you have the chance!
DescriptionAction: Will you attempt to claim the contents of the cargo?
